<br />
NEWS FLASH!  I played an SK during Kunark!  I remember what it was like being a second hand tank and having crap DPS.  I remember getting passed up for groups by lower level warriors.  Since PoP release knight have been the preferred tank for exp groups...Someone remind me how long thats been, a year maybe?<br />
<br />
